01:10:16,792 --> 01:10:18,708
Hei!

517
01:10:18,792 --> 01:10:20,292
Tetap di tempatmu.

518
01:10:22,292 --> 01:10:23,792
Minum saja tehmu.

519
01:10:26,624 --> 01:10:29,080
Kita harus lakukan sesuatu.
Kita tak bisa membawanya seperti ini.

520
01:10:29,832 --> 01:10:33,332
