01:37:11,580 --> 01:37:14,956
Kebohongan. Pembunuh.

679
01:37:19,916 --> 01:37:21,456
Kau orang baik.

680
01:37:23,000 --> 01:37:24,832
Kau orang jujur.

681
01:37:27,372 --> 01:37:30,332
